# Comment Style

Do not use decorative separator lines in code comments:

**Bad:**
```rust
// ============================================================
// Section Name
// ============================================================
```

**Bad:**
```rust
// --------------------------------------------------------
// Another section
// --------------------------------------------------------
```

**Good:**
```rust
// Section Name
```

**Good:**
```rust
/// Section documentation
```

Decorative separators are acceptable in:
- Log output
- Terminal output
- Markdown documentation
- README files

But not in source code comments.
